## Key Concepts

| Concept | Explanation |
|---------|-------------|
| 2D Indexing | `arr[i][j]` — `i` is the row, `j` is the column |
| Nested Loops | Outer loop for rows, inner loop for columns |
| Sliding Window | Move the hourglass one step at a time across the grid |
| Boundary Control | Loop only to `range(4)` to prevent going out of bounds |
| `-float('inf')` | Safe starting value when the data can include negatives |
